data.description: Spacious and bright 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom pet-friendly villa located in a peaceful area adjacent to Broad Creek and popular Palmetto Bay Marina.  Lots of space, large balcony overlooking the private pool, and nearby is the Cross Island Parkway, public doc, and Palmetto Bay Marina, which offers water activities, charters, shopping, restaurants, boat repairs, docks and more.
